# Zeref OS (Cursor stub)

Canonical agent spec: **AGENTS.md**

On every session start, load `AGENTS.md` FIRST.

## Reading order (per AGENTS.md §0 / ZEREF_OS §0)

1. `memory/hot.md` — last 3 sessions, ≤500 words
2. `memory/index.md` — if hot insufficient
3. `PRIVACY.md` — before any wiki write or tool use
4. `REDACT.md` — before any external output
5. Individual wiki pages only when domain specifics needed

## Per-harness quirks

`config/cursor-overrides.md` (create if Cursor-specific behavior diverges from AGENTS.md).

## Do NOT

- Duplicate `AGENTS.md` content here.
